{"id": 1860, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得香水营销中都有哪些可笑的地方？", "description": "不咋懂香水的人都没眼看！（题图来自: Public Domain）", "record_count": 11288, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170821161903Bf1dnwQUAGFZtoOl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-21T17:00:25Z", "questions": [{"id": 2823, "title": "你觉得香水营销中都有哪些可笑的地方？", "content": "你觉得香水营销中都有哪些可笑的地方？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 230529, "content": "强加人设，比如以“男友香”“雅痞男士”之类为卖点", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150019yYlMJEXWDdz01OQk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230530, "content": "推翻人设，“可攻可受”中性香，可以反串哦", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150101EI5ZMKa9TvtsORYi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230531, "content": "无论几年历史，每家都要弄一瓶邪乎的“传奇香”", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150233z05dl8UNotYnKJbL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230532, "content": "文案跟皇室沾亲带故，强调数百年历史", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150301WFBVzpD1C8NI4KQq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230533, "content": "没啥名的和烂大街的都爱管自己叫小众", "image": "img/option/option/20170820151317JyOPU6okN0YpRwCx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230534, "content": "为了强调用料珍贵，老是出现“几吨稀有植物才萃取出1ml原液”的赔本说法", "image": "img/option/option/201708201505168U2EAY6Wx3JZFVOs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230535, "content": "强贴标签，柑橘代表直率，木质代表深沉", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150549JmToBby9cDxKsgfe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230536, "content": "硬性按季节划分界限，春夏适合花果香，秋冬要喷辛香木质调", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150611yc8bGtNlLdOMKwHj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 230537, "content": "出一些“原味鸡”、“宜家”之类的猎奇味道香水", "image": "img/option/option/20170820150640dLPJt9406MSWRzBe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}